title: Rangers 1 Celtic 2: Scott Sinclair warns rivals his side will be even more ruthless after his late strike wins Old Firm derby and sends Brendan Rodgers’ side 19 points clear
text:
EFL GREAT SCOT Rangers 1 Celtic 2: Scott Sinclair warns rivals his side will be even more ruthless after his late strike wins Old Firm derby and sends Brendan Rodgers’ side 19 points clear 
Kenny Miller opened scoring for Rangers but Moussa Dembele pegged them back by WALLY DOWNES HR
